OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShocking abuse found across
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffire services - report     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Staff at a quarter of fire and rescue  
OL,6, services in England have reported      
OL,7, alleged racist, homophobic and         
OL,8, misogynistic behaviour in their ranks  
OL,9, in the past five years, inspectors say.
OL,11,FTheir report found bullying allegations
OL,12,Fin all services - and inspectors say   
OL,13,Fthis could be "the tip of the iceberg".
OL,15,FCases include male firefighters telling
OL,16,Fa colleague they would rape her and a  
OL,17,Fsenior officer using a racial slur.    
OL,19,FThe government called the findings     
OL,20,F"deeply concerning".                   
